featured_reviews.review_id:
Peaceful. Every Religious place I visit, whether it's a Temple. Mosque. Gurdwara. Buddha Vihar. Church.just love these places,
A beautiful and serene mosque. The masjid conducts religious programmes and best place in the area for eid prayers.,
This mosque follows Shafi school of Islam. It is air-conditioned on the ground floor. Facilities for wuzu is available on ground and first floor. The mosque is very spacious with total three floors for prayers.,
Alhamdulillah! Well design ablutions spaces and prayer halls.

featured_reviews.review_id: This is Shaf'ee masjid. So all namaz are at initial time (awwal waqt). Toilets are at ground floor. Filtered cold drinking water available. Masjid is amidst dense population hence very useful. Tabligi jamat works here. There is misbelief that Tabligi jamat means Deobandi. But the fact is people from all beliefs (maslak) do this work i.e. amrbilmaaruf and nahianilmunkar. This Shaf'ee masjid is good example.
